title: Breaking News: Cult Mom Lori Vallow children duct taped, wrapped in plastic, dismembered
itunes:title: Breaking News: Cult Mom Lori Vallow children duct taped, wrapped in plastic, dismembered
description:
JJ and Tylee, Lori Vallow's children have been found buried on husband Charles Daybell's property. Pings from the cellphone of Vallow's deceased brother led police to get a search warrant for the area. Alex Cox was at the property on two dates around the last time the children were seen.

Joining Nancy Grace today:

  • Ashley Willcott - Judge and trial attorney, Anchor on Court TV
  • Caryn Stark - NYC Psychologist
  • Sheryl McCollum - Forensics Expert & Cold Case Investigative Research Institute Founder
  • Dr. Kendall Crowns - Deputy Medical Examiner Travis County, Texas (Austin)
  • Nate Eaton, reporter East Idaho News
  • Ben Levitan - Telecommunications Expert
